sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as 用户
  participant Mobile as 移动端登录页
  participant Store as auth.store / SecureStore
  participant ApiClient as API Client
  participant AuthApi as AuthController
  participant AuthService as AuthService
  participant Jwt as JwtService
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant Me as UsersController

  User->>Mobile: 输入手机号
  Mobile->>AuthApi: POST /auth/code
  AuthApi->>AuthService: sendVerificationCode(phone)
  AuthService->>AuthService: 进程内保存 5 分钟验证码
  AuthService-->>AuthApi: expiresAt + devCode
  AuthApi-->>Mobile: 验证码响应

  User->>Mobile: 输入验证码并登录
  Mobile->>AuthApi: POST /auth/login
  AuthApi->>AuthService: login(phone, code)
  AuthService->>DB: upsert User
  AuthService->>Jwt: sign access token
  AuthService->>DB: 保存 refresh token hash
  AuthService-->>AuthApi: accessToken + refreshToken
  AuthApi-->>Mobile: TokenResponse
  Mobile->>Store: 保存 token 与登录态

  Mobile->>ApiClient: 请求受保护接口
  ApiClient->>Me: GET /me + Bearer accessToken
  Me->>DB: 查询 User 并计算 currentWeekId/currentQuarterId
  Me-->>ApiClient: UserContext
  ApiClient-->>Mobile: 恢复会话成功

  alt access token 过期
    ApiClient->>AuthApi: POST /auth/refresh
    AuthApi->>AuthService: refreshTokens(refreshToken)
    AuthService->>DB: 查找未吊销且未过期 token hash
    AuthService->>DB: 吊销旧 refresh token
    AuthService->>Jwt: 签发新 access token
    AuthService->>DB: 保存新 refresh token hash
    AuthApi-->>ApiClient: 新 token
    ApiClient->>Store: 更新 token
    ApiClient->>Me: 重试原请求
  else refresh 失败
    ApiClient->>Store: 清空登录态
    ApiClient-->>Mobile: 跳回登录
  end
